products.title: Valencia Orange Embers Roller Blind
products.description: Choose their striking orange roller blind to add a stunning splash of colour. Its as bright as bright can be. This blind will add a funky zing to any interior; think family rooms, breakfast rooms, rooms featuring strong blocks of colour as well as childrens bedrooms.

products.title: Valencia Orange Embers Vertical Blind
products.description: Make a bold, bright statement at your window with this vibrant valencia orange embers vertical blind. It has plenty of fun personality to really lift your home. Perfect for larger windows, this light filtering vertical fabric gives you maximum control. You can twist the vanes to make a bold, bright statement at your window with this vibrant valencia orange embers vertical blind.
